  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two killed in accident in Tangalle: Five in hospital",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Tangalle police said that two young people were killed and three others were injured when a car veered off the road and hit a banyan tree in the Thangalle Henakaduwa area.",
        "Lalith Sujeewa, a 35-year-old father of three from Virittamulla village, and Suresh Udayanga, a 30-year-old father of one, were killed in the accident.",
        "One person who was seriously injured in the accident is being treated at the Karapitiya Teaching Hospital and the other two at the Tangalle Base Hospital."
      ],
